344
00:35:24,249 --> 00:35:25,876
Au secours! Patron!

345
00:35:28,587 --> 00:35:29,671
Attention!

346
00:35:31,340 --> 00:35:32,382
Patron?

347
00:35:33,967 --> 00:35:35,010
