464
00:42:29,341 --> 00:42:31,385
La ferme!

465
00:42:31,468 --> 00:42:32,761
Obligez-moi.

466
00:42:34,972 --> 00:42:36,056
Qu'est-ce qui se passe?

467
00:42:36,139 --> 00:42:37,516
Je l'ignore.

468
00:42:42,062 --> 00:42:43,438
Adela...

